	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-lg-12">
			<h4 class="faq-subheader">This page explains the meaning of AML and KYC/CDD, and the steps which firms must take to remain compliant with the law, with a focus on the regulation relevant to firms operating in the United Kingdom.</h4>
		</div>
